CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. The entity that is a 'Nonreporting IGA FFI' is also treated as a registered deemed-compliant FFI under a 'Model 2' IGA, as defined in Part XII of IRS form W-8BEN-E.
